metadata.description:
Tribute to ᗩᒪᎧTTᗩ ᗰᎧᑎEY

Five layer stencil on wall. Out spraying in the dark again. The original painting is obviously not for sale.

The buyers will be given the right to use, distribute, and display the creation for non-commercial purposes only. Since the buyer owns this unique copy, they can also re-sell the creation on any secondary market.
